race.comment: FORTUNAS GIRL (15) is a first-starter by Divine Prophet out of Malionga. Ran fourth in a trial at Deagon over 1050m. This is not an overly strong contest and looks set for a bright start to her career. SECRET ROSE (13) finished eighth over 1212m at Coffs Harbour at her most recent appearance on September 4. Capable of playing a major role. VERY DEMURE (12) was in a rearwards position on the turn last time out before finishing 2.5 lengths from the winner in fourth over 1005m at Ballina. Looks to be in the right race to play a big role. BUBBLY MOON (3) finished second last start over 1000m at Nanango, beaten a long neck. Will be rock-hard fit and is worth plenty of thought.
